data.description: Welcome to luxury living in the Bentwater neighborhood! This stunning residence, just two years old, boasts an impeccable design with high-end finishes and hardwood floors throughout. With six spacious bedrooms, five full bathrooms and an office, this home offers an abundance of space for both family and guests. The gourmet kitchen includes top-of-the-line appliances, custom pantry, and a generous island and breakfast area. The separate dining room adds a touch of elegance, providing an ideal space for formal gatherings. The oversized primary suite is a true retreat. The primary bath is complete with a spa-like atmosphere, dual vanities, a luxurious oversized shower and soaking tub and two oversized walk-in closets. The fully finished basement is a true gem, designed to cater to a variety of needs. It features a bathroom, a bedroom, and a spacious living room. Additionally, you'll find a recreation room/bonus area, as well as ample storage to keep your space organized and clutter-free. The back yard is private and wooded with a deep property line for anyone that wants to expand to make more green space. The Bentwater golf community offers an array of amenities, including five swimming pools, tennis & basketball courts, pickleball, playgrounds, nature & biking trails, and a clubhouse. Its prime location ensures quick access to highways, top schools, plenty of shopping & dining, and much more. This home has all the features for your family to enjoy for many years! Don't miss the opportunity to make this like-new, luxury residence your dream home.
